                     <title xml:lang="en">Latin grant with Hebrew quitclaim</title>


                     
                     <note>
                        
                        <p>Latin grant of land by Radulph (Raoul) de Barkwith to Kirkstead Abbey in
                           Lincolnshire.</p>
                        
                        <p>Appended Hebrew quitclaim by Ursel ben Pucel of all the debts owed by
                           Ralph de Barkwith. </p>
                     
                     </note>


                  
                  </msItem>


               
               </msContents>


               
